{"tid":557540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際突發】載71人客機莫斯科墜毀 機員乘客生死未卜","createTime":"2018-02-11T12:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T13:46:28.000Z","uid":20058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3df5db395a3fe4ac33faf67b4d199db43f5b2ff2","tid":557540,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:44:04.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯傳媒報道，俄羅斯薩拉托夫航空（Saratov Airlines）一架載有71人的客機，在首都莫斯科附近墜毀，機員及乘客暫時生死未卜。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，肇事的客機為安托諾夫An-148，它從莫斯科多莫傑多沃國際機場起飛後，便從雷達上消失，當時共有載有65名乘客及6名機員，客機原定前往奧爾斯克（Orsk）。<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180211&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57821474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180211%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57821474&d=Vm%2BvChM2uigGI6EO2m2XksVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=06310ac6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180211%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57821474&h=78c90fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180211&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57821474</a>"},{"pid":"8efed468f79d4c517867e6e35ccb71942f33234a","tid":557540,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"mola mola =(<br />\n點解東歐好似成日都有飛機出事"},{"pid":"c0a6cd5e725d18a3f47404a71ffd17190f359d2f","tid":557540,"uid":162424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:46:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf97728f2e5cc1640f70229ddd5cd7f9a0f39b64","tid":557540,"uid":6305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"又黎 近排做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828daac0a4c51442fbe1bae2daf89a10f01befa2","tid":557540,"uid":162424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b8bebe5e57929139c233db8163df127d1e4d70e","tid":557540,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB